flowchart LR
    C[客户端] --> G[API Gateway]
    G --> A[Go 秒杀接入服务]

    A -->|Lua预占| R[(Redis)]
    R --> RS[reservation Hash]
    R --> DZ[待发送ZSET]

    A -->|即时发送| M[(RocketMQ)]
    S[Reservation补发扫描器] --> DZ
    S -->|同一message_id重发| M

    M --> OC[订单消费者]
    OC -->|本地事务| P[(PostgreSQL)]

    P --> I[consumer_inbox]
    P --> INV[sku_inventory]
    P --> O[orders]
    P --> IR[inventory_reservation]
    P --> L[inventory_ledger]
    P --> OB[event_outbox]

    OR[Outbox Relay] --> OB
    OR -->|至少一次发送| M2[(RocketMQ事件Topic)]

    M2 --> RP[Redis状态投影消费者]
    RP --> R

    M2 --> CW[补偿消费者]
    CW --> CT[compensation_task]
    CW -->|Lua条件补偿| R

    RC[对账服务] --> R
    RC --> P
    RC --> M
    RC --> RT[repair_task / 人工工单]
